    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This car is in great condition and has been well-maintained, making it a fantastic choice for anyone seeking quality and performance. While you might find some minor, expected signs of use, it remains a solid and dependable vehicle ready for many more miles. Don't miss out on this well-cared-for gem!",
